i5.las2peer.classLoaders.helpers

Class LibraryVersion

  • java.lang.Object
    • i5.las2peer.classLoaders.helpers.LibraryVersion
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<LibraryVersion>

    public class LibraryVersion
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<LibraryVersion>
    a simple class managing a library version number in the format major.minor.subversion-build where minor, subversion and build are optional
